=== Patient/Encounter Specific
Do not request translation for AVSs. Instead communicate verbally. Use https://cchmc.service-now.com/is?id=kb_article_view&sysparm_article=KB0013699[Epic templated translations] when available.

Do not translate progress notes, reports, or test results. To provide this in writing to families, summarize them in a letter using words the family can easily understand and request translation of the letter via the https://centerlink.cchmc.org/forms/interpreter-services/written-translation-request[Translation Request Form on CenterLink].

Translation is not currently available for sending MyChart message, text messages, or emails to families. If you receive a message in a language other than English, call the family with a <<outbound-phone-calls,phone interpreter>> or request a translation from the https://centerlink.cchmc.org/forms/interpreter-services/written-translation-request[Translation Request Form on CenterLink].

For any other patient/encounter specific translations, contact CONTACT NEEDED to start the process. We will consider the importance of the materials and other resources which could serve this purpose.
