== Language Access Research
Consult Language Access Services when planning research projects related to language access or with participants who use a language other than English.

Include the cost of translation in your budget. Translating consent forms costs about $100 per page. 

Work with translations@cchmc.org to get a more accurate cost estimate. This is especially important if you need transcription, videos, or instrument validation.